8173:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV8: ETRP frequency divided by 8.
8174:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  TIM_ExtTRGPolarity The external Trigger Polarity.
