8176:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_INVERTED: active low or falling edge active.
8177:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_NONINVERTED: active high or rising edge active.
